---
export interface Props {
	title?: string;
	bgcolor?: string;
	id?: string;
}
const { title, bgcolor, id } = Astro.props;
---

<div class={bgcolor} id={id}>
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl py-14 px-10 text-center">
		<h2 class="underline-4xl text-4xl font-bold">{title}</h2>
		<div class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-10 md:flex-row lg:pt-5">
			<div class="flex basis-1/2 flex-col justify-center lg:basis-1/3">
				<img src="/together.svg" class="w-52 place-self-center" />
				<div class="text-center text-raisin">
					<span class="font-zen text-lg uppercase">Together</span>
					<p class="pt-4 leading-loose">
						Team spirit is the foundation for a strong team and a successful company. We strive to make all team members feel comfortable. That's why we focus on
						collaboration, trust and support within the team. This includes respect, empathy, and support.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="flex basis-1/2 flex-col justify-center lg:basis-1/3">
				<img src="/ownership.svg" class="w-52 place-self-center" />
				<div class="text-center text-raisin">
					<span class="font-zen text-lg uppercase">Ownership</span>
					<p class="pt-4 leading-loose">
						It is important to us that our employees learn, develop, and feel challenged at The Oater without feeling overwhelmed or left alone. Therefore, each team
						member takes responsibility over projects, and always receives support and regular feedback.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-10 md:flex-row lg:pt-10">
			<div class="flex basis-1/2 flex-col justify-center lg:basis-1/3">
				<img src="/goodvibes.svg" class="w-52 place-self-center" />

				<div class="text-center text-raisin">
					<span class="font-zen text-lg uppercase">Good Vibes</span>
					<p class="pt-4 leading-loose">
						At The Oater, we are optimistic and have a positive attitude. We believe that striving for a shared vision does not only bring us together but should also
						be fun.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="flex basis-1/2 flex-col justify-center lg:basis-1/3">
				<img src="/gratitude.svg" class="w-52 place-self-center" />
				<div class="text-center text-raisin">
					<span class="font-zen text-lg uppercase">GRATITUDE</span>
					<p class="pt-4 leading-loose">
						We are mindful and show appreciation for ourselves and others. We are humble, appreciative and celebrate each other (and ourselves) for our successes.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="flex basis-1/2 flex-col justify-center lg:basis-1/3">
				<img src="/care.svg" class="w-52 place-self-center" />

				<div class="text-center text-raisin">
					<span class="font-zen text-lg uppercase">Care</span>
					<p class="pt-4 leading-loose">
						All our actions have consequences and affect those around us and our environment. Therefore, we make all our decisions striving towards a more livable
						future on this planet for all.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
